miss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Teams List</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/my-teams.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters my teams list"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >Add New Teams, Review Team List</h4> <p>Each time a new project or queue is created a team is created too. The team is automatically staffed with the project or ticket queue roster. Add new members to the team simply by adding new them to the roster of the project or queue.</p></div></div><span id="pmTeam"></span> <div class="media panel"> <a class="pull-right media-object" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#pmteam"><img src="img/pm-team-myteams.png" alt="TeamHeadquarters project team management" width="300" height="139"></a> <div class="modal fade" id="pmteam" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="pmteam" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>Project Team Management</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/pm-team-myteams.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters my teams list"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >Project Team Management</h4> <p>Every project has My Teams integrated providing complete Team management to the Project Manager. Add new members to the team by adding them to the project roster. View and create schedule entries into team member calendars, view and modify time sheets, print time sheet reports and view individual ticket loads.</p></div></div><span id="tmCalendar"></span> <div class="media panel"> <a class="pull-right media-object" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#tmcal"><img src="img/tm-calendar.png" alt="TeamHeadquarters project team management" width="300" height="139"></a> <div class="modal fade" id="tmcal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="tmcal" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Teams - Member Calendar Management</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/tm-calendar.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters my teams member calendar"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >My Teams - Member Calendar Management</h4> <p>My Teams, member calendar management is available from Projects and Queues. Open a team-members calendar and view schedules or schedule work on tickets, tasks and custom events.</p></div></div><span id="tmTimesheet"></span> <div class="media panel"> <a class="pull-right media-object" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#tmtime"><img src="img/tm-timesheet.png" alt="TeamHeadquarters project time sheet management" width="300" height="139"></a> <div class="modal fade" id="tmtime" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="tmtime" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Teams - Member Time Sheet Management</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/tm-timesheet.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters my teams time sheet"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >My Teams - Member Time Sheet Management</h4> <p>My Teams, member time sheet management is available from Projects and Queues. Open a team-members time sheet and view time sheet entries or add entries for tickets, tasks and custom events.</p></div></div><span id="tmTimesheetRpt"></span> <div class="media panel"> <a class="pull-right media-object" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#tmsht"><img src="img/timesheet-report.png" alt="TeamHeadquarters project time sheet report" width="300" height="139"></a> <div class="modal fade" id="tmsht" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="tmsht" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Teams - Member Time Sheet Report</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/timesheet-report.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters my teams time sheet report"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >My Teams - Member Time Sheet Report</h4> <p>My Teams, member time sheet report is available from Projects and Queues. Open a team-members time sheet report and view time sheet entries for the period selected. Download the report as a PDF, CSV, RTF, TIFF, or web archive.</p></div></div><span id="tmTicsAssigned"></span> <div class="media panel"> <a class="pull-right media-object" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#TicsAssigned"><img src="img/tickets-assigned.png" alt="TeamHeadquarters tickets assigned" width="300" height="139"></a> <div class="modal fade" id="TicsAssigned" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="TicsAssigned" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Teams - Tickets Assigned</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/tickets-assigned.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters tickets assigned"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >My Teams - Tickets Assigned</h4> <p>My Teams "tickets assigned" functionality provides a complete list of tickets assigned to the team member selected. Drill into details, or query the team member to determine status, time estimates, etc...</p></div></div><span id="tmMemberAvailabilty"></span> <div class="media panel"> <a class="pull-right media-object" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#MemberAvailabilty"><img src="img/teammember-availability.png" alt="TeamHeadquarters team member availability" width="300" height="139"></a> <div class="modal fade" id="MemberAvailabilty" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="MemberAvailabilty" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Teams - Tickets Assigned</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/teammember-availability.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters team member availability"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >My Teams - Member Availability</h4> <p>My Teams review the total available hours minus tasks assigned and provides the user with the team member's availability over an 8 week future window. This prediction is accurate and takes the guesswork away from task assignment.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="footer"> <?php include '../public_html/includes/footer.html';?> </div></body></html>